Haryana
Nov 02, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A 12-year-old girl was allegedly raped by her neighbour at Surajkund area here, police said today.

In her complaint, the victim alleged that Sadanand, 50, came to her house yesterday when she was alone and raped her, they said.

Hearing the girl's cries, her grandmother and neighbours rushed to her rescue following which the accused fled from the spot, police said.


